longBusinessSummary: Wildsky Resources Inc. focusing on acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Africa. The company holds three exploration licenses for niobium-tantalum exploration; and seven exploration licenses for gold and lead-zinc exploration in Nigeria. Its exploration license covering an area of 742 square kilometers. The company was formerly known as China Minerals Mining Corporation and changed its name to Wildsky Resources Inc. in August 2018. Wildsky Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
